Developer Terms of Use
des:
Are you tired most of the time and don’t know when was the last time you fed your baby? Do you feel like there should be easier to do this?

We got your back! Just tell Alexa to ask Sweet Nanny to log feeding and you always ask for the information about the last time you fed the baby.
